(Oops I forgot Nightlight could fly.)

::Aerotaur::
    He walked up to Nightlight and explained to her what was going on.  He 
transformed into his bird mode and waited for Perplex to return with Trinity. 
 "Nightlight, why don't you carry the children while I carry Perplex, Gramps, 
and Termitron.  Windlord will carry some supplies and we can make a second 
trip for the rest."
